sub_title: Area Sales Manager - Ukraine, Romania, Moldova
summary:
Sales and project manager by occupation, musician and specialist in Russian studies by education.  
At work involved, creative and well-organized. 
At leisure traveller and enthusiast of healthy lifestyle.
Focused on constant self-improvement, discovering new horizons and living in the harmony with the surrounding world. 
Since 2009 lives in The Netherlands. 
Recipient of "Pole of the Year 2011 in The Netherlands" award in category - Culture.
